TASK
Write ONE LinkedIn DM that:
- Cites exactly ONE concrete detail from NOTES.
- Optionally weaves in title/company/location if present.
- Makes ONE light ask.
- Ends with a question.
Plain text only, ≤450 chars, no added facts beyond NOTES/FIELDS.
